Config::LDAPClient
------------------

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the following modules:

    Net::LDAP (optional, unnecessary if you never call ->connect)
    Moose
    MooseX::AttributeHelpers


